{"tid":1932091,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"疫情開始在東南亞擴散","createTime":"2020-03-18T13:46:50.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-18T13:51:32.000Z","uid":68430,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"6502fa4abccbebba415035e6d4d44de6d59fad7c","tid":1932091,"uid":68430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-18T13:46:50.000Z","msg":"西班牙疫情增至近600人不治 疫情開始在東南亞擴散<br />\n<br />\n歐洲的新型肺炎疫情持續，西班牙單日再多超過2500人確診，累計死亡人數增至近600人。疫情亦開始在東南亞多國蔓延。馬來西亞警告，如果民眾不遵守出行限制，確診人數將會「海嘯式」增加。<br />\n<br />\n2020-03-18 21:42:5<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/joinchat/EUB2V1TmmnYAI0NMn-w_1Q\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fjoinchat%2FEUB2V1TmmnYAI0NMn-w_1Q&d=AthmRk%2BBSDjaWf6zT95BzLY5fiapVNQoBN5VkmpLYQk%3D&h=5cd5e34d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/joinchat/EUB2V1TmmnYAI0NMn-w_1Q</a>"},{"pid":"3b8524d3315ce3c963f6c2f7d7ecdb86ff4b4d84","tid":1932091,"uid":120431,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-18T13:51:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}